name: Pro Domestics
overview:
Pro Domestics, Inc. expertise is matching and connecting the right people with the right positions – whether they are for a full-time career opportunity or a travel assignment. They are committed to develop long-term relationships with their clients and job seekers, with a shared goal of mutual success. It is their top priority to ensure both parties are satisfied. They also take the time to understand the unique skill requirements of each client.

Their objective is to understand each client’s requirements for candidate’s skills, education and experience. They take time to get to know each professional individually (talents, personal and career goals)in order to place them in the correct environment. This unique personalized approach and their professional staff helps to create a perfect match for all our clients.

Pro Domestics, Inc. has been successfully been staffing the following Industries with Specialties in:

Domestic Industry (caregivers, nannies, housekeepers), Accounting/Finance, Medical/Health, Engineering, Construction, Energy, Environmental, Administrative, Hospitality, Information Technology, Manufacturing,IT, Human Resources, Data Mining and Analytics, Security/Protective Services, Sales/Retail/Business Development, Legal, Education/Training,Executive/General Management, Materials Management, Administrative, Sales and Marketing
